This is a placeholder for the NZ Family Road Trip Packing Checklist PDF.
The real PDF will be generated separately and dropped in at this path
(static/downloads/nz-family-roadtrip-packing-list.pdf) so the download
route already exists and the email-gated lead magnet works end to end.

Contents to include when generated (40+ items):
- Clothing (layers, rain jackets, swimwear, sun hats, sturdy shoes)
- Documents (passports, licence, insurance, bookings, cash)
- Car/Campervan (chargers, offline maps, water bottles, car seats, snow chains)
- Kids' entertainment (tablets+headphones, games, colouring, soft toys, journal)
- First aid (plasters, paracetamol, antihistamine, SPF50+, sandfly repellent)
- Snacks (muesli bars, fruit, trail mix, drink bottles, chilly bin)
